{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01StGWWV2Wi2KThXWQ2tuSvN","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Comprehensive Analysis Summary:\n\n1. Project Structure:\n   - Multimodule Maven project\n   - Modules: roster-common, roster-boot\n   - Uses Spring Boot and H2 in-memory database\n   - Java 17 targeted\n\n2. Key Files:\n   a) Dockerfile: Custom image based on maven:3.9.12-ibm-semeru-21-noble\n      - Installs uv (micromamba alternative)\n      - Sets up Python venv\n      - Installs Playwright\n      - Builds and runs Spring Boot application\n\n   b) Application Configuration (application.properties):\n      - H2 in-memory database\n      - Server port: 8080\n      - Hibernate DDL auto-update\n      - SQL logging enabled\n      - H2 console enabled\n      - PrimeFaces theme: saga\n\n   c) Main Application: RosterApplication.java\n      - Standard Spring Boot application\n      - Scans entities from jakartaee.tutorial.roster.entity\n      - Enables JPA repositories in spring.tutorial.roster.repository\n\n3. Source Code Locations:\n   - Entity classes: roster-boot/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/entity/\n   - Repositories: roster-boot/src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/repository/\n   - REST Controller: roster-boot/src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/rest/RosterController.java\n   - Utility classes: roster-common/src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/util/\n\n4. Repositories/Entities:\n   - Entities: League, Player, Team, SummerLeague, WinterLeague\n   - Repositories: LeagueRepository, PlayerRepository, TeamRepository\n\n5. Additional Notes:\n   - No docker-compose files found\n   - Test files present but not extensively explored in this summary\n\nWould you like me to provide more detailed contents of specific files or dive deeper into any particular aspect of the project?"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2c11cb83-6ba2-4880-b8f2-f05df9ef97a7","uuid":"e9f645b8-0f56-4d18-8278-0973705e535e"