al/roster/util/*.java: DTOs and exception (unchanged, moved)\n- src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/entity/*.java: JPA entities (unchanged, moved)\n- smoke.py: 47 smoke tests covering all REST endpoints\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- roster-boot/ (entire module directory)\n- roster-common/ (entire module directory)\n- roster-boot/pom.xml, roster-common/pom.xml\n- roster-boot/src/main/java/spring/tutorial/roster/RosterApplication.java (Spring Boot main class)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 0 blocking errors\n- **Docker Image Conflicts:** During testing, the `$SCARF_IMAGE_TAG` was overwritten by a parallel evaluation run. Resolved by using a unique image tag for testing, then rebuilding with the expected tag.\n- **No compilation errors, no test failures**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":494,"cache_read_input_tokens":116953,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":494,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":731},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2c11cb83-6ba2-4880-b8f2-f05df9ef97a7","uuid":"0f3af919-9850-42fb-bec4-5f9d67677a19"}
